news.title: Shop buyers on par with other housing society members: Bombay HC
news.para: The divisional joint registrar had confirmed a Sept 2022 dy registrar order which directed inclusion of names of 12 shopkeepers as society members.

news.title: Mohali: Sohana building collapse inquiry report indicts building owners, contractor
news.para: The two proprietors, Gagandeep Singh and Parminder Singh, residents of Chao Majra village in Mohali district, were initially arrested but subsequently released on bail.

news.title: Maharashtra: Property registration offices to work extra hours from March 1 to handle rush
news.para: The registration department issued a notification in this regard late on Monday evening. "All 519 registration offices across the state will operate for extra two hours from March 1," a senior official told TOI on Tuesday.

news.title: Uttarakhand HC seeks rehabilitation plan over slum demolishment in Haldwani
news.para: A bench comprising Chief Justice G Narendar and Justice Ashish Naithani was hearing a public interest petition challenging the "unannounced demolition" of the settlements.

news.title: Gujarat HC dismisses contempt plea in housing redevelopment case
news.para: The court found the applications "frivolous" and determined they were primarily aimed at obstructing the ongoing redevelopment process.

news.title: EOW files closure report in Mack Star fraud case against HDIL ex-promoters
news.para: It was alleged that the Wadhawans cheated Mack Star Marketing by illegally selling the aforementioned properties without consent of the majority shareholder (DE Shaw Group, which holds 83.36% shares) of Mack Star Marketing.

news.title: Housing minister supports Madhya Pradesh's urban development initiatives
news.para: Khattar spoke during a session titled ‘Unlocking Land Values and Cities,' emphasising growth targets for 2047. Key initiatives include expanding Bhopal and Indore Metro rail systems, promoting e-mobility and providing affordable housing.

news.title: Ahmedabad: In two years, 150 redevelopment projects finalised amid challenges
news.para: The push for new and modern homes is stronger than ever, as residents of aging housing societies increasingly embrace redevelopment. Yet, despite the momentum, hurdles remain — ranging from hesitant residents and unrealistic expectations to market slowdowns and policy uncertainties.

news.title: New home sales in USA drop 10.5% in January 2025
news.para: ​The steep decline in new home sales, reported by the Commerce Department on Wednesday, also likely reflected the impact of snowstorms and extremely cold weather in much of the country last month.

news.title: Bengaluru civic body settles 19-year-dispute over public utility building rent
news.para: A BBMP official stated that for the past 50 years, several floors of PUB and the Tower Block have been leased on a rental and contract basis, with rents significantly lower than private buildings on MG Road.

news.title: Star Cement proposes Rs 3,200 crore plant in Assam
news.para: The state government also signed a Rs 500-crore MoU with Global Health Ltd, while two non-financial agreements were signed with ITE Education Service.

news.title: Sundaram Home Finance to foray into Telangana for emerging business segment
news.para: EB comprises small business loans of up to Rs 20 lakh for small shops and businesses and affordable housing finance where the company provides loans of up to Rs 35 lakh, SHF said in a statement here on Tuesday.

news.title: Bengaluru: Raghavendra Layout residents oppose factories causing pollution
news.para: Apart from air pollution, residents are also worried about the discharge of chemicals such as grease, paint and oil into the drainage system, which could impact groundwater.

news.title: Swiggy moves to new office in Gurugram, maintain its headquarters in Bengaluru
news.para: Swiggy's main competitor, Zomato, previously operated its headquarters in the same building. However, the company vacated the premises in late 2018.

news.title: Indonesia's central bank to provide funding of $7.9 billion for state housing project
news.para: During last year's election campaign, Prabowo had pledged his government would build 3 million affordable houses per year.

news.title: DM asks fire department to enhance earthquake readiness in Noida
news.para: While seismologists said the earthquake was not of a very high magnitude, its depth of just around 5km and epicentre at Dhaula Kuan in New Delhi, caused stronger reverberations.

news.title: Embassy Developments to raise up to Rs 2,000 crore through QIP
news.para: The fundraising may involve equity shares, convertible or exchangeable securities, Global Depository Receipts, American Depository Receipts, Foreign Currency Convertible Bonds, and other instruments.

news.title: South Delhi’s real estate potential now worth Rs 5.65 lakh crore: Report
news.para: According to the data, around 18,446 plots are available across the 42 Cat A, B & C colonies in South Delhi whose size ranges from 125 sq. yd. to 1750 sq. yd. at an average price of Rs 6- 15 lakh per square yard.

news.title: Baashyam Constructions comes onboard as the associate sponsor for Chennai Super Kings
news.para: A renowned name in the real estate sector, Baashyaam Constructions is known for its innovative approach, cutting-edge design, and exceptional architectural expertise.

news.title: Kolkata civic body demolishes 150 illegal buildings in a year
news.para: The KMC building department lodged 500 FIRs against unscrupulous promoters, said mayor Firhad Hakim on the concluding day of the KMC budget for the financial year 2025-26.
